This code system http://hl7.org/fhir/datestype defines the following codes:

CodeDisplayDefinition
card-issued Card IssuedThe date when an insurance card was issued.
claim-received Claim ReceivedThe date when an insurer nreceived a claim, pre-authorization or predetermination.
service-expected Service ExpectedThe date or period on or during which the services are expected to be performed.
